                    "description",
                    "Open-source credential recovery tool used by ALPHV affiliates to extract passwords stored by browsers, email clients, databases, and Windows credential stores. LaZagne supplements Mimikatz by recovering application-layer credentials that are not accessible via LSASS dumping, broadening the pool of valid accounts available for lateral movement."
